reviews.review_text: Last SOTM EVER!!! Last SOTM EVER ! ! ! !

Rain Tape I was able to take my very good friend Cork Nelms to this show.  Funny thing, Cork had a strange resemblance to Jerry and was born in the mid 50's.  The lovely ladies that ran the concession at 3 Rivers were instructed to card everyone for beer.  Cork forgot his ID and I had to buy all of his libations.  It did not bother him even though it rained like hell from the end of the 1st set to the 2nd set.  To this day he thanks me for getting him back to see the Dead before the passing of Jerry.  It's funny what becomes important to you when you get older.  More Dead!
